    "/orders/search": {
      "post": {
        "description": "Search and retrieve orders using filter parameters such as order `type`, status, date range, and more. This endpoint allows customers and merchants to query past orders for review, analysis, or support. <p> Filters must be provided in the request body. You can paginate results using `offset` and `limit`. If pagination parameters are not specified, the default response returns up to 10 orders. </p>",
